  "2026-06-25T20:44:39.414Z",codex-gpt5,"Manual smoke evidence: in an isolated temp project with PM_PATH and PM_GLOBAL_PATH, initialized a tracker, scaffolded ./context-kit with package init --capability commands, installed it project-scope, ran package describe --project --markdown --output docs/context-kit-reference.md, verified the file was non-empty and contained Package surface reference, context-kit, and Commands, and verified --output emitted no stdout. A second isolated smoke also verified --quiet --output writes nested parent directories."
